# React Standards

## Defaults

- Function components only
- React 19 patterns as used in the repo (`useActionState`, `useTransition`, etc.)
- Do not add `useMemo` / `useCallback` by default unless the project already relies on them or a measured problem exists
- Extract hooks for reused stateful logic; keep domain components readable

## Client boundaries

`"use client"` only where needed (forms, tables with client state, stores). Do not mark entire trees client for convenience.

## State

Prefer server data + URL/search params. Use Zustand / React Query only as the project already does — don’t introduce a second global state library.
